Uchenna Jennifer Eze (Ọmụmụ: Uche Eze, 26 Julai 1984)  bŲ nwafor óbódò naijiria nke ēji ntá akukó nke igwe komputa were mara
Obukwa onye okacha mara na ihe gbasara edemede nkpakorita uka, ma burukwa ezigbo onye ojiego achu ego
Obu onye isi na ulo oru nke ana akpo BellaNaija, nke eji nta akuko, edemede nakwa nkwakorita uka nke ndi mmadu
na afo 2014, ulo oru nta  akuko forbes tinyere aha ya nime onu ogu mmadu iri ato nke na agba mbo puru oke iche nime Africa.
